<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
</head>
<body class="nabe-page trastoo">
        <div class="wrap">
            <header class="header">
                <% include ../partials/header %>
            </header>
            <div class="header__banner">
                <h1 class="header__title" data-loc="">Contacto</h1>
                <p class="header__tagline apercu">
                 Utiliza el siguiente formulario de contacto para hacernos llegar cualquier cosa que consideres oportuna, sugerencias, incidencias, mejoras, opiniones...ten por seguro que revisamos todos los mensajes y respondemos a la mayor brevedad posible para satisfacer tu consulta. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <input type="hidden" value="#F5F5F1" id="nabe_color">
            <nav class="control-views view__select">
                <div class="view__icon now view__current">
                    <svg class="circle-border" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 72 72"><g fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.879" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-miterlimit="10"><path d="M10.3 30.7c1.4-1.8 3.7-.3 3.7 1.6 0 1.1-.8 1.9-.8 3s1.2 1.8 1.2 3.1-.6 1.7-.6 3.3.9 1.8.6 3.7c-.2 1.9-2.4 2.8-3.5 1-1.1-1.8.2-3 .2-4.3-.1-1.3-1.1-1.9-1.1-3.5s.8-2 .8-3.7-2.2-1.9-.5-4.2zM43.2 29.2c0 2.1-.5 3.5-3.9 3.5s-3.9-1.3-3.9-3.5 1.7-3.9 3.9-3.9 3.9 1.8 3.9 3.9z" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"></path><path d="M47.5 22.9c-.1-2.5-2.4-1.5-3.6-3.2-1.2-1.7.3-6.8-4.5-6.8S36 18 34.9 19.7c-1.2 1.7-3.5.7-3.6 3.2-.1 2.5 2.9 2.4 2.9 2.4h10.6c-.2 0 2.8.1 2.7-2.4zM30.5 42.8v4.7h18V32.8H30.7" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"></path><path d="M31.5 24h-5.9c-.4 0-.7.3-.7.7V33M24.9 43v9.4c0 .4.3.7.7.7h27.7c.4 0 .7-.3.7-.7V24.7c0-.4-.3-.7-.7-.7h-6.1" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"></path><path d="M13.9 34.7c2 0 4-.3 5.9-.9 4.5-1.3 9.3-1.1 13.7.7l7.6 3.1c-.1 1.2-1.2 2-2.3 1.7l-7-1.8" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"></path><path d="M13.9 40.8l3.8-.2c1.8-.2 3.6.3 5 1.3 1.6 1.1 3.5 1.6 5.4 1.3l4.5-.7c-.2-1.3-1.4-2.2-2.7-2.1l-1.4.2c-.7.1-1.4-.4-1.6-1.1-.2-.7.2-1.4.9-1.7 1.2-.5 2.6-.5 3.8-.2" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"></path></g></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="view__text">
                    <h2>Contacto</h2>
                </span>
            </nav>
            <div class="isotope__wrapper">
               <div class="panel isotope" id="isotope" style="position:relative;">
                <form action="http://localhost:2007/contacto" method="POST">
                    <div style="width:50%;text-align:center;float:left;padding-left:10px;">
                        <label>Nombre</label><input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="<% if (perfil.doc.name){%><%= perfil.doc.name%><%}%>">
                    </div>
                    <div style="width:50%;text-align:center;float:right;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;">
                        <label>Apellidos</label><input type="text" id="surename" name="surename" value="<% if (perfil.doc.surename){%><%= perfil.doc.surename%><%}%>">
                    </div>
    				<div style="width:50%;text-align:center;float:left;padding-left:10px;">
                        <label>Email</label><input type="text" id="email" name="email" value="<%= perfil.doc.email%>">
                    </div>
                    <div style="width:50%;text-align:center;float:right;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;">
                        <label>Asunto</label><input type="text" id="subject" name="subject">
                    </div>
    				<div style="width:100%;text-align:center;float:left;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;">
                        <label>Consulta</label><textarea id="query"  name="query"></textarea> 
                    </div>
                    <div width="100%" style="text-align:center;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:30px;">
                        <button onclick="submit();">Enviar</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        <footer>
            <% include ../partials/footer %>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>